Name: change donation link

description: the admin would be able to change to link to the payment site

players: admin

preconditions: logged in as admin

Basic flow:
  1) click on menu
  2) menu shows up 
  3) click on admin setting
  4) admin settings show up
  5) enter link into change link input
  6) click save
  7) confirm window shows up
  8) click confirm 

alternate flow:
  8) click on cancle 
  9) original link is shown in the link input

exception flow:
  if the link that was put is invalid the link input turns red and a message appears

post conditions: the link to the payment site was changed
